  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">When markdown-validator runs in your CI/CD pipeline, it acts as a
  quality gate on every pull request. If any Required rule fails, the pipeline
  exits with a non-zero code and blocks the merge until you fix the reported
  issues.</shortdesc>

  <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="conbody:1;28:12">

    <section id="ci-workflow" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="section:1;30:31">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="title:2;31:14">How it works</title>

      <fig id="fig-ci-flow" class="- topic/fig " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="fig:1;33:29">
        <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="title:3;34:16">Pull-request validation flow</title>
        <image href="../../images/ci-integration-flow.png" placement="break" class="- topic/image " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="image:1;35:78">
          <alt class="- topic/alt " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="alt:1;36:16">Flowchart: author pushes a commit, CI checks out the branch,
          installs markdown-validator, runs md-validate validate, then branches
          on exit code. Exit 0 means the PR is eligible to merge. Exit 1 blocks
          the merge; the author reads the failure report, fixes the file, pushes,
          and the pipeline re-runs.</alt>
        </image>
      </fig>

      <ol class="- topic/ol " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="ol:1;44:11">
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="li:1;45:13">Push a commit or open a pull request.</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="li:2;46:13">CI runs <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;46:29">md-validate validate docs/ --rules rules/tutorial.json</codeph>
        (exact paths vary — check <filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="filepath:1;47:45">.github/workflows/validate-docs.yml</filepath>).</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="li:3;48:13">Exit <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="codeph:2;48:26">0</codeph>: all Required rules pass — PR is eligible to merge.</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="li:4;49:13">Exit <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="codeph:3;49:26">1</codeph>: a Required rule failed — merge is blocked. Fix the
        failures shown in the log, push again, pipeline re-runs.</li>
      </ol>

      <note type="tip" class="- topic/note " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="note:1;53:24">Run validation locally before opening a pull request to
      catch failures before CI does. Use the same <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="codeph:4;54:59">--rules</codeph> path
      that CI uses — both must point to the same committed file, or results will
      differ.</note>
    </section>

    <section id="setup-ci" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/concepts/c_ci-integration-overview.dita" xtrc="section:2;59:28">
